only its visual form (image\\/photo). Each image, more than aesthetic becomes ecstatic (ecstasy and static).<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"462\":{\"type\":\"pullQuoteImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"\\u201c...Like bubbles in water, that can\\u2019t help but float to the surface and inevitably burst.\\u201d\",\"file\":[\"449\"],\"size\":\"medium\"}},\"463\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>We would also like to point out that while the \\u201clike\\u201d legitimizes and constructs an aura, it also destroys it through its own excedent. Images fall thanks to their own weightlessness. They fall by virtue of reaching such great popularity.<br><br><br>Like bubbles in water, that can\\u2019t help but float to the surface and inevitably burst.<br><br><br>Thanks to our subscription to these dynamics (guilty as charged), we\\u2019re destined to maneuver in a precarious transit from bubble to bubble, just below the surface where they burst, forced to slow down their ascension and try to make it last forever.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"465\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Designs\\u2019 representation in its image form in the web, is like an empty postcard, with no content, no address or addressee; postamp from nowhere. A letter sent by no one, whose sole purpose is to circulate at the fastest speed possible around every circuit available. Its postage stamp says \\u201cstamp\\u201d, engraved on a thick, textured, acid-free cotton paper grown in certified fields.<br><br><br>Perhaps its contents read: Lorem ipsum dolor sit amen.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"464\":{\"type\":\"pullQuoteImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"\\u201cDesigns\\u2019 representation in its image form in the web, is like an empty postcard, with no content, no address or addressee\\u201d\",\"file\":[\"452\"],\"size\":\"medium\"}},\"468\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p><em>Response #1 written by Roberto Salazar,&nbsp;Creative Director, Mexico.<\\/em><\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\"}},\"466\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h2>DOING THINGS DIFFERENTLY&nbsp;<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em><br><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Services Unknown is an open-ended Superimpose Studio project that facilitates new ideas, discussion, events and product.<\\/em><\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\"}}},\"52\":\"Communication dwells in two different realms: its manifest (palpable) expression and its latent expression. \\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nNowadays, when we subscribe to social media platforms we agree to terms and conditions for their services; which manifest the legal conditions that are required in order for us to enjoy the use of any given platform (legal pressure)\",\"37\":[\"450\"]}}', '2017-07-07 15:30:56', '2017-07-07 15:30:56', '1846c098-c665-4120-a038-9d74a04fce6e'),
