 ('412', '570', '2', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Parley\",\"slug\":\"parley\",\"postDate\":1509532828,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"34\":\"adidas Originals\",\"4\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Brief\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Deliver creative for adidas Originals\' first collaboration with Parley. Target a new audience that are disconnected from Parley, create a conversation between the Originals lifestyle and Parley mission.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"center\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=8c9tB66UMWU\",\"thumbnail\":[\"565\"]}},\"new3\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Response\",\"textContent\":\"<p>We stepped away from the approach of trying to teach and educate about the ocean with stats and predictions. We focussed communications on bridging the gap between concrete and ocean and talking in a language engaging to the audience.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Commissioning a spoken-word artist from our target audience to create a powerful call to action piece, we used this as the backbone of a narrative to create a mixed media film that showcased the product, the adidas Originals lifestyle and the ocean. Bringing everything together for the first time in a new and dynamic way for the brands.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"new7\":{\"type\":\"twoImagesOneImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"largeImage\":[\"567\"],\"smallImages\":[\"568\",\"569\"],\"position\":\"largeImageLeft\"}}},\"37\":[\"563\"],\"51\":\"top\",\"36\":\"full\",\"35\":\"FW 17\"}}', '2017-11-01 10:40:28', '2017-11-01 10:40:28', '6564a859-f100-4767-8b34-06e2bd6d5a8e'),
