 ('442', '570', '2', '1', 'en_us', '25', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Parley\",\"slug\":\"parley\",\"postDate\":1509532800,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"34\":\"adidas Originals\",\"4\":{\"605\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"606\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"571\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Brief\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Deliver creative for adidas Originals\' first collaboration with Parley. Target a new audience that are disconnected from Parley, create a conversation between the Originals lifestyle and Parley mission.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"center\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"603\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"601\",\"602\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"573\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Response\",\"textContent\":\"<p>We stepped away from the approach of trying to teach and educate about the ocean with stats and predictions. We focussed communications on bridging the gap between concrete and ocean and talking in a language engaging to the audience.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Commissioning a spoken-word artist from our target audience to create a powerful call to action piece, we used this as the backbone of a narrative to create a mixed media film that showcased the product, the adidas Originals lifestyle and the ocean. Bringing everything together for the first time in a new and dynamic way for the brands.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"572\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=8c9tB66UMWU\",\"thumbnail\":\"\"}},\"575\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Artist collaborations\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Taking our core strategy further than the film, we commissioned 3 international artists to create a series of works that artistically interpreted the campaign message. These were integrated alongside further call to action statements.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The artist\'s work took center stage alongside a custom built installation at Frieze art fair in London alongside being released as a digital zine on adidas.com<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"595\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"578\",\"568\",\"579\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"596\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"580\",\"581\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"597\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"584\",\"586\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"599\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"591\",\"588\",\"592\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"600\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"593\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}}},\"37\":[\"563\"],\"51\":\"top\",\"36\":\"full\",\"35\":\"FW 17\"}}', '2017-11-01 12:14:12', '2017-11-01 12:14:12', '6d532170-687b-4969-a096-aa78f20c7d80'),
 ('443', '551', '2', '1', 'en_us', '4', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"ARSHAM\",\"slug\":\"daniel-arsham\",\"postDate\":null,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"34\":\"adidas Originals\",\"4\":{\"617\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"BRIEF\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Introduce adidas Originals first artist collaboration, educate the audience about Daniel Arsham and bring the art and streetwear worlds together.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"618\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"RESPONSE\",\"textContent\":\"<p>We decided to play on the concept of the internet hacking by creating a treasure hunt of content. Centered around an anonymous phone number where a hacker revealed secret conversations from the making of the Daniel Arsham film, whilst simultaneously leaking dynamic multimedia content onto an anonymous hub and hacked into Daniel\\u2019s very own social channels.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>All exposing Daniel Arshams creative process to the world and revealing the project gradually, keeping people guessing until the product was finally revealed as a surprise at the end.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"619\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"610\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"624\",\"625\",\"626\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"620\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"613\",\"612\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":\"\",\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}}},\"37\":\"\",\"51\":\"top\",\"36\":\"full\",\"35\":\"2017\"}}', '2017-11-01 12:23:15', '2017-11-01 12:23:15', 'cd0f1350-7051-4ddd-a6cd-0c42c83b3541'),
