 ('471', '682', '4', '1', 'en_us', '7', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"The Studio Reports 001 - INERTIA\",\"slug\":\"inertia\",\"postDate\":1509550080,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"53\":{\"683\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"656\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"684\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"657\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"685\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"658\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"686\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"659\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"687\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"660\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"688\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"661\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"689\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"662\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"690\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"663\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"691\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"664\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"692\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"665\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"693\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"666\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"694\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"667\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"695\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"668\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"696\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>WE ALL HAVE OUR OWN REALITIES<br>The Studio Reports is an open-minded Superimpose Studio project that embraces individual realities and creative contribution to visual culture.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Submissions to&nbsp;<a href=\\\"mailto:hello@superimpose-studio.com\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">hello@superimpose-studio.com<\\/a><\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}}},\"52\":\"For our first The Studio Reports report, we have chosen the theme of Inertia.\\r\\n\\r\\nBrought about by an apathy induced by the overexposure to everything, it is the antithesis to the chaos and turmoil that surrounds us.\\r\\n\\r\\nWhen the future offers little promise, and the past feels forever lost, the only solace seems to be in finding a state of stasis.\\r\\n\\r\\nIn what feels like a game of checkmate from the start, the desire to move forward doesn\\u2019t seem quite so appealing. Welcome to anxiety, laziness and the rejection of consciousness.\",\"37\":[\"656\"]}}', '2017-11-02 14:04:19', '2017-11-02 14:04:19', 'daf853d8-e3d5-4b72-af38-0cfa03b9c56d'),
 ('472', '609', '2', '1', 'en_us', '13', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Pusha T\",\"slug\":\"bodega-babies\",\"postDate\":1509537540,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"34\":\"adidas Originals\",\"4\":{\"621\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"614\",\"615\",\"616\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"622\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Brief\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Deliver creative for adidas Originals final collaboration with Pusha T, an EQT ADV shoe called \\u2018Bodega Babies\\u2019. Draw inspiration from the product story of growing up around Bodegas to create a compelling film.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"623\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=qCDtXnhfiNI\",\"thumbnail\":\"\"}},\"643\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Response\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Taking on the distinct elements of the product and talent, we produced a 2.46 minute video that conveyed realness, exploration and the importance of community. Heavily playing on Pusha T\\u2019s experience of life in his early days, it pays tribute to the neighbourhood corner store, a proving ground for growth and evolution, showcasing different people and generations and telling these stories in a different way.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"634\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"633\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"638\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"636\",\"637\",\"635\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"642\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"640\",\"641\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"644\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Beyond the film, we created the overall campaign identity and concept based on NYC Bodegas which applied across title cards, press materials, in-store installations and an exclusive event hosted by Pusha T.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"650\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"647\",\"645\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"651\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"648\",\"646\",\"649\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"654\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"653\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"position\":\"center\"}}},\"37\":[\"608\"],\"51\":\"top\",\"36\":\"full\",\"35\":\"FW 17\"}}', '2017-11-02 14:04:53', '2017-11-02 14:04:53', 'dfa149e8-972a-494e-aafa-6ea48877d540'),
 ('473', '570', '2', '1', 'en_us', '28', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Parley\",\"slug\":\"parley\",\"postDate\":1509532800,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"34\":\"adidas Originals\",\"4\":{\"605\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"606\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"571\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Brief\",\"textContent\":\"<p>In adidas Originals first collaboration with Parley, an organisation where creators, thinkers and leaders raise awareness for our oceans, Superimpose Studio were tasked to deliver core creative and communications materials in order to generate meaningful conversation driven by the product release.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"center\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"603\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"601\",\"602\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"573\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Response\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Stepping away from the stale approach of preaching through statistics and predictions, we focused the message on bridging the divergence between concrete and ocean and talking in a language that resonated with the adidas consumer. Youthful, creative and passionate.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Commissioning a spoken word artist to create a powerful call to action, this would serve as the backbone of the campaign narrative. With supporting mixed media heroing the product through films, social content and impactful imagery, we showcased the adidas Originals lifestyle and the eco-innovation message in an integrated form making a serious topic relevant and engaging.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"572\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=8c9tB66UMWU\",\"thumbnail\":\"\"}},\"575\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Artist collaborations\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Championing emerging talent across all disciplines, we identified and collaborated with a handful of international creatives passionate about sustainability and oceans to interpret the campaign message artistically. They generated a series of original works that tied with the call to action statements to reinforce the message.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The original works took centre stage alongside a custom built installation at Frieze Art Fair in London, also released as a digital zine on adidas.com<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"595\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"578\",\"568\",\"579\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"596\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"580\",\"581\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"597\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"584\",\"586\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"655\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"588\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"599\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"591\",\"592\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"600\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"593\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}}},\"37\":[\"563\"],\"51\":\"top\",\"36\":\"full\",\"35\":\"FW 17\"}}', '2017-11-02 14:05:08', '2017-11-02 14:05:08', '8a86d8f5-195e-4350-9dec-003d4b5c7047'),
