 ('555', '543', '2', '1', 'en_us', '18', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Mini Rodini\",\"slug\":\"mini-rodini\",\"postDate\":1509642960,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"34\":\"adidas Originals\",\"4\":{\"561\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"558\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"544\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"BRIEF\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Deliver a creative that pulls from the collections graphic inspirations whilst maintains an adidas Originals attitude.<br><\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"549\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=frstQG0eSvw\",\"thumbnail\":\"\"}},\"560\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"RESPONSE\",\"textContent\":\"<p>We created a lookbook in stills and film that encapsulated the playfulness of the collaboration collection whilst maintaining a style that stayed true to the adidas Originals brand values.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>To create this we shot on location in South Africa as a way of directly reflecting the patterns and inspiration from the collection. The locations providing us with a unique background for our street-cast kids to explore and conquer in their unique way.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"545\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"539\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"733\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"717\",\"540\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"562\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"559\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"550\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=S4ntq-U6zI0\",\"thumbnail\":\"\"}},\"547\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"ena