 ('561', '682', '4', '1', 'en_us', '17', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"The Studio Reports Inertia\",\"slug\":\"inertia\",\"postDate\":1509550080,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"53\":{\"683\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"656\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"684\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"657\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"685\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"658\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"686\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"659\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"687\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"660\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"728\":{\"type\":\"pullQuote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"When the future offers little promise, and the past feels forever lost, the only solace seems to be in finding a state of stasis.\"}},\"688\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"661\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"689\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"662\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"690\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"663\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"691\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"664\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"729\":{\"type\":\"pullQuote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"In what feels like a game of checkmate from the start, the desire to move forward doesn\\u2019t seem quite so appealing. Welcome to anxiety, laziness and the rejection of consciousness.\"}},\"692\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"665\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"693\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"666\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"694\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"667\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"695\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"668\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"696\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>WE ALL HAVE OUR OWN REALITIES<br>The Studio Reports is an open-minded Superimpose Studio project that embraces individual realities and creative contribution to visual culture.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Submissions to&nbsp;<a href=\\\"mailto:hello@superimpose-studio.com\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">hello@superimpose-studio.com<\\/a><\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}}},\"52\":\"For our first The Studio Reports report, we have chosen the theme of Inertia.\\r\\n\\r\\nBrought about by an apathy induced by the overexposure to everything, it is the antithesis to the chaos and turmoil that surrounds us.\",\"37\":[\"656\"]}}', '2017-11-06 17:02:21', '2017-11-06 17:02:21', '7b214b02-72ad-4b4f-8dc9-d828405f03e8'),
 ('562', '493', '4', '1', 'en_us', '17', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"PERSPECTIVES 001: POST-TRUTH\",\"slug\":\"post-truth\",\"postDate\":1508561040,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"53\":{\"494\":{\"type\":\"pullQuote\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"\\u2018Beyond or superseding the importance of truth; pertaining to an era or situation when truth is no longer significant or relevant; usually in a pejorative sense, uncaring of factual accuracy.\\u2019\"}},\"495\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>For Services Unknowns first creative showcase, we&nbsp;created&nbsp;a visual exploration into the polarity between perceived truths and factual evidence. This was&nbsp;our view of what is happening in the world through artist escape.<br><br>In a time of post truths, nothing can be trusted and everything can be questioned. For all the changes happening&nbsp; in the world there is a multitude of reactions. These could be real, or they could have been fabricated by us&hellip;<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"499\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"498\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"496\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Hosted in The 100 Room on The Rooftop of&nbsp;The&nbsp;Ace Hotel&nbsp;London, the space&nbsp;became&nbsp;a&nbsp;creative&nbsp;territory for the pressing topics of now.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong><br><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Fake news<br>Content saturation<br>Culture stagnation<br>Gender and identity<br>Political turbulence<br><br><\\/strong>Playing with these themes through subjective&nbsp;interpretation, we had the freedom to create a physical space that breeds curiosity and critical thinking, stretching the imagination and&nbsp;eliciting&nbsp;emotional responses from visual cues.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"500\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"497\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"520\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>The&nbsp;showcase&nbsp;spanned across&nbsp;various forms of art and media, from graphics, fabrics, animation to photography and sound, with attendees having the opportunity to view, interact and take a piece of the work home.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>With hundreds of people coming together to one space from all corners of the industry and beyond, we sparked conversation,&nbsp;criticism, and a new discourse for the future.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"507\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"504\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"508\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"505\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"511\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"510\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"509\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"506\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"514\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"512\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"515\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"513\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"517\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"516\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"519\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"518\"],\"size\":\"large\"}}},\"52\":\"Perspectives is a Services Unknown series which looks to open discussion around key themes and subjects that influences and shape the development of creativity, community and society.\\r\\n\",\"37\":[\"492\"]}}', '2017-11-06 17:02:33', '2017-11-06 17:02:33', 'd6d305ab-015b-4a97-b536-4f760157df96'),
 ('563', '551', '2', '1', 'en_us', '19', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"DANIEL ARSHAM - PAST\",\"slug\":\"daniel-arsham\",\"postDate\":1509642840,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"34\":\"adidas Originals\",\"4\":{\"740\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"739\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"617\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"BRIEF\",\"textContent\":\"<p>In adidas Originals\\u2019 first ever artist collaboration with renowned American talent Daniel Arsham, Superimpose Studio\\u2019s mission was to bring the art and streetwear worlds together in order to expose the collaborative take on the archive shoe.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"708\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/youtu.be\\/H5Y7xbC_JlA\",\"thumbnail\":\"\"}},\"618\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"RESPONSE\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Informed by the artist\\u2019s enduring fascination with archeology, discovery and \\u2018found objects\\u2019, we distilled this as the core concept driving the campaign strategy and creative. Playing with the notion of internet hacking, we created a digital treasure hunt through \\u2018found\\u2019 content. The campaign centred around an anonymous phone number revealed secret conversations alluding to upcoming film directed by the artist, whilst simultaneously leaking material onto an anonymous online hub as an insight into his creative process.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Through a carefully orchestrated campaign which revealed the project gradually, we kept people guessing until the final reveal.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"619\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"610\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"627\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"697\"