 ('566', '609', '2', '1', 'en_us', '35', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Pusha T - SHORT FILM\",\"slug\":\"bodega-babies\",\"postDate\":1509643080,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"34\":\"adidas Originals\",\"4\":{\"621\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"615\",\"616\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"622\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Brief\",\"textContent\":\"<p>In the final instalment of a collaboration series between adidas Originals and Pusha T, Superimpose Studio had to elevate the story behind the \\u2018Bodega Babies\\u2019 EQT ADV shoe, drawing inspiration from the product and Pusha T\\u2019s coming of age around his local place of importance to create a compelling film.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"623\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=qCDtXnhfiNI\",\"thumbnail\":\"\"}},\"643\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Response\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Taking on the distinct elements of the product and talent, we produced a 2.46 minute video that conveyed realness, exploration and the importance of community. Heavily playing on Pusha T\\u2019s experience of life in his early days, it pays tribute to the neighbourhood corner store, a proving ground for growth and evolution, showcasing different people and generations and telling these stories in a different way.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"727\"]}},\"634\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"633\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"638\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"636\",\"637\",\"635\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"642\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"640\",\"641\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"719\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"e