 ('590', '833', '2', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"#747warehousest\",\"slug\":\"747warehousest\",\"postDate\":null,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"34\":\"adidas\",\"4\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"BRIEF\",\"textContent\":\"<p>The yearly NBA All-Star Weekend is one of the biggest moments in the global sport and cultural calendar. The objective was to launch 747 Warehouse in Los Angeles into the forefront of everyone\\u2019s minds through bold, unapologetic and customisable visual language that appealed as much to the celebrities and press as it did to consumers.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Response\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Superimpose Studio led the creative and art direction of a \\u2018\\u2019No Rules\\u2019 approach that drove the brand language and visual identity across this competitive and noisey period - setting it apart from the usual ASW offerings and cementing the legacy of adidas as a creator\\u2019s brand.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The anti-corporate aesthetic carried throughout the entire space: immersive installations for product collaborations, machines building Speedfactory AM4s on the spot, test centres to show off your skills, the Sound Lab, the Stage and Creator Pop-up customisation stations as well as building walls, and floor takedowns.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Mimicking a sticker pack of assets, the experience was created purposefully to allow visual elements to stand alone as well as integrate with each other. Treating graphics and iconography as \\u2018collectables\\u2019, attendees could create their own versions of 747 merchandise and apparel.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"new3\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Outcome\",\"textContent\":\"<p>#747warehousest was mentioned across social 6x more than rival Nikes #makersofthegame activation.<\\/p><p>Ensured adidas owned the conversation around All Star Weekend with 42% share of voice over a 30 day period.<\\/p><p>Creating a 100%&nbsp;neutral to positive sentiment amongst an attendance of over 20,000.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}}},\"37\":[\"832\"],\"51\":\"top\",\"36\":\"full\",\"35\":\"2018\"}}', '2018-03-05 17:05:37', '2018-03-05 17:05:37', '5e9b6465-f95a-47b3-a490-5bee3fc1fda6'),
 ('591', '798', '2', '1', 'en_us', '7', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"adidas Originals by Neighborhood\",\"slug\":\"ao_nbhd\",\"postDate\":null,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"34\":\"adidas Originals\",\"4\":{\"799\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"783\",\"769\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"800\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"BRIEF\",\"textContent\":\"<p>adidas Originals by Neighborhood is one of the most revered collaborations on the planet. Superimpose were tasked with creating an eclectic campaign that celebrated the collaborations core inspiration that arose from the original Japanese Shinsengumi, whilst making it relevant for today\'s audience.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"782\"]}},\"801\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/youtu.be\\/8h9iMMv0ETs\",\"thumbnail\":[\"785\"]}},\"802\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Response\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Flipping the expected approach of looking at the collection inspirations in a nostalgic way. Superimpose took key traits from the Shinsengumi such as the \\u2018ride of die\\u2019 collective attitude they had for each other and their unique way of combining east and west styles.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Taking these and bringing them into today and towards the future. Showcasing what the contemporary Shinsengumi would look like. Bringing forward the mix of styles & races that encapsulate the new generation. <\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Delivering this in a visually stunning film that heightens the senses and drives the collection home to the audience.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"778\"]}},\"803\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"765\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"804\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\"