 ('601', '833', '2', '1', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"#747warehousest\",\"slug\":\"747warehousest\",\"postDate\":null,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"34\":\"adidas\",\"4\":{\"862\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"BRIEF\",\"textContent\":\"<p>The yearly NBA All-Star Weekend is one of the biggest moments in the global sport and cultural calendar. The objective was to launch 747 Warehouse in Los Angeles into the forefront of everyone\\u2019s minds through bold, unapologetic and customisable visual language that appealed as much to the celebrities and press as it did to consumers.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"863\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Response\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Superimpose Studio led the creative and art direction of a \\u2018\\u2019No Rules\\u2019 approach that drove the brand language and visual identity across this competitive and noisey period - setting it apart from the usual ASW offerings and cementing the legacy of adidas as a creator\\u2019s brand.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The anti-corporate aesthetic carried throughout the entire space: immersive installations for product collaborations, machines building Speedfactory AM4s on the spot, test centres to show off your skills, the Sound Lab, the Stage and Creator Pop-up customisation stations as well as building walls, and floor takedowns.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Mimicking a sticker pack of assets, the experience was created purposefully to allow visual elements to stand alone as well as integrate with each other. Treating graphics and iconography as \\u2018collectables\\u2019, attendees could create their own versions of 747 merchandise and apparel.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"864\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Outcome\",\"textContent\":\"<p>#747warehousest was mentioned across social 6x more than rival Nikes #makersofthegame activation.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Ensured adidas owned the conversation around All Star Weekend with 42% share of voice over a 30 day period.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Creating a 100%&nbsp;neutral to positive sentiment amongst an attendance of over 20,000.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":\"\"}}},\"37\":[\"885\"],\"51\":\"top\",\"36\":\"full\",\"35\":\"2018\"}}', '2018-03-06 14:42:23', '2018-03-06 14:42:23', 'e85f4029-92b2-4b63-a74d-1f1ed545a151'),
