e\":[\"896\"]}},\"928\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"895\",\"886\",\"894\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"929\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Results\",\"textContent\":\"<p>#747WarehouseSt was mentioned 6x more than Nike\\u2019s #makersofthegame during All-Star weekend, with over 20k attendees to the event. It led above all brands with 42% share of voice over the 30 day span around NBA All-Star, achieving a monumental outcome for adidas\\u2019 ASW history.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"897\"]}},\"930\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":\"\",\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"931\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Stage\",\"textContent\":\"<p>The yearly NBA All-Star Weekend is one of the noisiest moments in the global sport and cultural calendar. The objective was to launch 747 Warehouse in Los Angeles into the forefront of everyone\\u2019s minds through a bold, unapologetic and customisable brand identity and incredible creative activations that appeal as much to the celebrities and press as it did to consumers.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"900\"]}},\"932\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"902\",\"901\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"933\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Merchandise\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Bespoke 747 branding was created for all merch from welcome packs to hoodies and celebrity specials. Customisation stations created with our modular branding allowed attendees to create their own through touch screen monitors, creating personal variations for keeps.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"924\"]}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"948\",\"950\",\"943\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"935\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Fresh Produce\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Custom print shoes, each cut out of larger graphics and built by robots on the spot, delivered \\u2018fresh\\u2019 produce straight to consumers in an innovative first from the brand.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"951\"]}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"952\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"new3\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"945\",\"953\",\"944\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"936\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Basketball\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Branding played an integral role to the main spectacle of the whole weekend. The Hip-Hop&nbsp;East vs West Basketball game.&nbsp;Played on a bespoke court and terraces, with each team of stars sporting their own custom kits.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"946\"]}},\"new4\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"954\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"new5\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"956\",\"957\",\"955\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}}},\"37\":[\"885\"],\"51\":\"top\",\"36\":\"full\",\"35\":\"2018\"}}', '2018-03-06 20:15:53', '2018-03-06 20:15:53', '76fb55ba-87d5-4909-a2db-9982d618f932'),
 ('609', '833', '2', '1', 'en_us', '11', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"#747warehousest\",\"slug\":\"747warehousest\",\"postDate\":null,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"34\":\"adidas\",\"4\":{\"925\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"885\",\"888\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"862\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"BRIEF\",\"textContent\":\"<p>The yearly NBA All-Star Weekend is one of the noisiest moments in the global sport and cultural calendar. The objective was to launch 747 Warehouse in Los Angeles into the forefront of everyone\\u2019s minds through a bold, unapologetic and customisable brand identity and incredible creative activations that appeal as much to the celebrities and press as it did to consumers.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"958\"]}},\"927\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Response\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Superimpose Studio led the creative and art direction of a \\u2018\\u2019No Rules\\u2019 approach that drove the brand language and visual identity across this competitive period - setting it apart from the usual ASW offerings and cementing the legacy of adidas as a creator\\u2019s brand.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The anti-corporate aesthetic carried throughout the entire space: immersive installations for product collaborations, machines building Speedfactory AM4s on the spot, test centres to show off your skills, the Sound Lab, the Stage and Creator Pop-up customisation stations as well as building walls, and floor takedowns.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Mimicking a sticker pack of assets, the experience was created purposefully to allow visual elements to stand alone as well as integrate with each other. Treating graphics and iconography as \\u2018collectables\\u2019, attendees could create their own versions of 747 merchandise and apparel.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"imag