heading\":\"Fresh Produce\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Custom print shoes, each cut out of larger graphics and built by robots on the spot, delivered \\u2018fresh\\u2019 produce straight to consumers in an innovative first from the brand.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"951\"]}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"952\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"new3\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"945\",\"953\",\"944\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"936\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Basketball\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Branding played an integral role to the main spectacle of the whole weekend. The Hip-Hop&nbsp;East vs West Basketball game.&nbsp;Played on a bespoke court and terraces, with each team of stars sporting their own custom kits.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"946\"]}},\"new4\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"954\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"new5\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"956\",\"957\",\"955\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}}},\"37\":[\"885\"],\"51\":\"top\",\"36\":\"full\",\"35\":\"2018\"}}', '2018-03-06 20:15:55', '2018-03-06 20:15:55', '9f8bf519-c080-459a-90c9-6a3602b58732'),
 ('610', '830', '2', '1', 'en_us', '8', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Burberry\",\"slug\":\"burberry\",\"postDate\":null,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"34\":\"Burberry\",\"4\":{\"831\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"822\",\"845\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"849\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"brief\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Ideation and creative direction for an online experience with standout visual imagery to elevate the new Burberry Rainbow Capsule Collection. Conveying the product in a brave, bold and futuristic way that speaks out to a younger audience.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"827\"]}},\"850\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Reponse\",\"textContent\":\"<p>With noise surrounding the drop of every Burberry collection, Superimpose decided to take the creative in a new direction most luxury brands shy away from. We created visual content to live in a virtual time capsule - a space to revisit, experience the clothing, memories and energy that came with it.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Producing a shoot packed with personality, energy and youthfulness, we then ripped up the rule book of how to showcase premium product by collaging them together in various patterns and textures to create looks that stand out from the crowd.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"824\"]}},\"851\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"811\",\"813\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"852\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"829\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"position\":\"right\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Going a step further, we developed a bank of 3D assets that showcased the Burberry patterns in a distinct way using rotating fruits and impactful slogans. Another layer was added by creating eye-catching GIFS that combined brand patterns, model movements and 3D assets.<br><br>These visuals then layered together into a unique 3D interactive experience that mimicked the the experience of a time capsule in the future - launching a showpiece for Burberry that injected the brand into new audiences through a refreshing new route.<span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"828\"]}},\"853\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"820\",\"812\",\"817\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"883\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"882\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"876\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"875\",\"874\",\"872\"],\"size\":\"6\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"854\":{\"type\":\"twoImagesOneImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"largeImage\":[\"838\"],\"smallImages\":[\"846\",\"848\"],\"position\":\"largeImageLeft\"}},\"855\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"826\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"856\":{\"type\":\"twoImagesOneImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"largeImage\":[\"819\"],\"smallImages\":[\"847\",\"837\"],\"position\":\"largeImageRight\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"823\",\"836\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}}},\"37\":[\"811\"],\"51\":\"top\",\"36\":\"half\",\"35\":\"2018\"}}', '2018-03-06 20:23:50', '2018-03-06 20:23:50', '50147e6e-d942-453a-badf-fd7ccea64b91'),
