 ('618', '833', '2', '1', 'en_us', '12', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"#747warehousest\",\"slug\":\"747warehousest\",\"postDate\":null,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"34\":\"adidas\",\"4\":{\"925\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"885\",\"888\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"862\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"BRIEF\",\"textContent\":\"<p>The yearly NBA All-Star Weekend is one of the noisiest moments in the global sport and cultural calendar. The objective was to launch&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/maps.google.com\\/?q=747+Warehouse&entry=gmail&source=g\\\">747 Warehouse<\\/a>&nbsp;in Los Angeles into the forefront of everyone\\u2019s minds through a bold, unapologetic and customisable brand identity and incredible activations that appeal as much to the celebrities and press as it did to consumers.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"958\"]}},\"927\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Response\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Superimpose Studio led the creative concept and art direction of a \\u2018\\u2019No Rules\\u2019 approach that drove the brand language and visual identity across this competitive period - setting it apart from the usual NBA&nbsp;All-Star Weekend&nbsp;offerings and cementing the legacy of adidas as a creator\\u2019s brand.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The anti-corporate aesthetic carried throughout the entire space: immersive installations for product collaborations, machines building individualised footwear&nbsp;on the spot, test centres to show off your skills, the Sound Lab, the Stage and Creator Pop-up customisation stations as well as building walls, and floor takedowns.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Mimicking a sticker pack of assets, the experience was created purposefully to allow visual elements to stand alone as well as integrate with each other. Treating graphics and iconography as \\u2018collectables\\u2019, attendees could create their own versions of 747 merchandise and apparel.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"896\"]}},\"928\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"895\",\"886\",\"894\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"929\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Results\",\"textContent\":\"<p>#747WarehouseSt was mentioned 6x more than Nike\\u2019s #makersofthegame during All-Star weekend, with over 20k attendees to the event. It led above all brands with 42% share of voice over the 30 day span around NBA All-Star, achieving a monumental outcome for adidas\\u2019 ASW history.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"897\"]}},\"930\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":\"\",\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"931\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Stage\",\"textContent\":\"<p>The yearly NBA All-Star Weekend is one of the noisiest moments in the global sport and cultural calendar. The objective was to launch 747 Warehouse in Los Angeles into the forefront of everyone\\u2019s minds through a bold, unapologetic and customisable brand identity and incredible creative activations that appeal as much to the celebrities and press as it did to consumers.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"900\"]}},\"932\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"902\",\"901\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"933\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Merchandise\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Bespoke 747 branding was created for all merch from welcome packs to hoodies and celebrity specials. Customisation stations created with our modular branding allowed attendees to create their own through touch screen monitors, creating personal variations for keeps.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"924\"]}},\"964\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"948\",\"950\",\"943\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"935\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Fresh Produce\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Custom print shoes, each cut out of larger graphics and built by robots on the spot, delivered \\u2018fresh\\u2019 produce straight to consumers in an innovative first from the brand.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"951\"]}},\"965\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"952\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"966\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"945\",\"953\",\"944\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"936\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Basketball\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Branding played an integral role to the main spectacle of the whole weekend. The Hip-Hop&nbsp;East vs West Basketball game.&nbsp;Played on a bespoke court and terraces, with each team of stars sporting their own custom kits.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"946\"]}},\"967\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"954\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"968\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"956\",\"957\",\"955\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}}},\"37\":[\"885\"],\"51\":\"top\",\"36\":\"full\",\"35\":\"2018\"}}', '2018-03-07 09:20:08', '2018-03-07 09:20:08', 'f27930e1-65e7-4b90-86ad-df5eca48545c'),
 ('619', '830', '2', '1', 'en_us', '10', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Burberry\",\"slug\":\"burberry\",\"postDate\":null,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"34\":\"Burberry\",\"4\":{\"831\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"822\",\"845\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"849\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"brief\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Ideation and creative direction for an online experience with standout visual imagery to elevate the new Burberry Rainbow Capsule Collection. Conveying the product in a brave, bold and futuristic way that speaks out to a younger audience.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"827\"]}},\"850\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Reponse\",\"textContent\":\"<p>With noise surrounding the drop of every Burberry collection, Superimpose decided to take the creative in a new direction most luxury brands shy away from. We created visual content to live in a virtual time capsule - a space to revisit, experience the clothing, memories and energy that came with it.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Producing a shoot packed with personality, energy and youthfulness, we then ripped up the rule book of how to showcase premium product by collaging the visuals&nbsp;together in various patterns and textures to create looks that stand out from the crowd.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"824\"]}},\"851\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"811\",\"813\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"852\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"829\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"position\":\"right\"}},\"971\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Going a step further, we developed a bank of 3D assets that showcased the Burberry patterns in a distinct way using rotating fruits and impactful slogans. Another layer was added by creating eye-catching GIFS that combined brand patterns, model movements and 3D assets.<br><br>These visuals then layered together into a unique 3D interactive experience that mimicked the the experience of a time capsule in the future - launching a showpiece for Burberry that injected the brand into new audiences through a refreshing new route.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"828\"]}},\"853\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"820\",\"812\",\"817\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"883\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"882\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"876\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"875\",\"874\",\"872\"],\"size\":\"6\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"854\":{\"type\":\"twoImagesOneImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"largeImage\":[\"838\"],\"smallImages\":[\"846\",\"848\"],\"position\":\"largeImageLeft\"}},\"855\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"826\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"856\":{\"type\":\"twoImagesOneImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"largeImage\":[\"819\"],\"smallImages\":[\"847\",\"837\"],\"position\":\"largeImageRight\"}},\"972\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"823\",\"836\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}}},\"37\":[\"811\"],\"51\":\"top\",\"36\":\"half\",\"35\":\"2018\"}}', '2018-03-07 09:20:25', '2018-03-07 09:20:25', 'eb5a58c3-711c-4dfe-9f41-bc23dbde5dcd'),
 ('620', '798', '2', '1', 'en_us', '16', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"adidas Originals by Neighborhood\",\"slug\":\"ao_nbhd\",\"postDate\":null,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"34\":\"adidas Originals\",\"4\":{\"799\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"783\",\"769\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"800\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"BRIEF\",\"textContent\":\"<p>adidas Originals by Neighborhood is one of the most revered collaborations on the planet. Superimpose were briefed with&nbsp;creating&nbsp;an eclectic campaign that celebrates the collaboration\\u2019s core inspiration of the traditional Japanese Shinsengumi, whilst making it relevant for today\'s audience.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"782\"]}},\"801\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/youtu.be\\/8h9iMMv0ETs\",\"thumbnail\":[\"785\"]}},\"802\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Response\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Rejecting the expected approach of shooting the collection\\u2019s inspirations with a nostalgic lens, Superimpose focused on key traits from the Shinsengumi such as the \\u2018ride or die\\u2019 collective attitude they had for each other and their unique way of fusing eastern and westing&nbsp;styles.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"778\"]}},\"803\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"765\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"804\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"784\",\"779\",\"776\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"805\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"773\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"806\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Bringing these values into the present and pushing into the future, we showcased what the contemporary Shinsengumi looks like by integrating the diverse mix of styles and race that encapsulate the new generation.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Delivered in a visually striking film that heightens the senses and puts the squad mentality at the forefront of the story, we created an accompanying lookbook that elevated the product from a global perspective<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"881\"]}},\"878\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"793\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"808\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"792\",\"787\",\"790\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"865\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"OUTCOME\",\"textContent\":\"<p>The film and photography premiered at a series of launch parties from LA to Tokyo, whilst pop-up stores delivered the product to the consumer ending with the entire collection achieving global sell-out.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"767\"]}},\"809\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"860\",\"858\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"810\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"766\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"861\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":\"\",\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}}},\"37\":[\"765\"],\"51\":\"top\",\"36\":\"full\",\"35\":\"2018\"}}', '2018-03-07 09:21:44', '2018-03-07 09:21:44', '1f60a730-89ad-4835-bbb8-efc27506b760'),
 ('621', '833', '2', '1', 'en_us', '13', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"#747warehousest\",\"slug\":\"747warehousest\",\"postDate\":null,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"34\":\"adidas\",\"4\":{\"925\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"885\",\"888\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"862\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"BRIEF\",\"textContent\":\"<p>The yearly NBA All-Star Weekend is one of the noisiest moments in the global sport and cultural calendar. The objective was to launch&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/maps.google.com\\/?q=747+Warehouse&entry=gmail&source=g\\\">747 Warehouse<\\/a>&nbsp;in Los Angeles into the forefront of everyone\\u2019s minds through a bold, unapologetic and customisable brand identity and incredible activations that appeal as much to the celebrities and press as it did to consumers.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"958\"]}},\"927\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Response\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Superimpose Studio led the creative concept and art direction of a \\u2018\\u2019No Rules\\u2019 approach that drove the brand language and visual identity across this competitive period - setting it apart from the usual NBA&nbsp;All-Star Weekend&nbsp;offerings and cementing the legacy of adidas as a creator\\u2019s brand.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The anti-corporate aesthetic carried throughout the entire space: immersive installations for product collaborations, machines building individualised footwear&nbsp;on the spot, test centres to show off your skills, the Sound Lab, the Stage and Creator Pop-up customisation stations as well as building walls, and floor takedowns.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Mimicking a sticker pack of assets, the experience was created purposefully to allow visual elements to stand alone as well as integrate with each other. Treating graphics and iconography as \\u2018collectables\\u2019, attendees could create their own versions of 747 merchandise and apparel.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"896\"]}},\"928\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"895\",\"886\",\"894\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"929\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Results\",\"textContent\":\"<p>#747WarehouseSt was mentioned 6x more than Nike\\u2019s #makersofthegame during All-Star weekend, with over 20k attendees to the event. It led above all brands with 42% share of voice over the 30 day span around NBA All-Star, achieving a monumental outcome for adidas\\u2019 ASW history.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"897\"]}},\"930\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":\"\",\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"931\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Stage\",\"textContent\":\"<p>The yearly NBA All-Star Weekend is one of the noisiest moments in the global sport and cultural calendar. The objective was to launch 747 Warehouse in Los Angeles into the forefront of everyone\\u2019s minds through a bold, unapologetic and customisable brand identity and incredible creative activations that appeal as much to the celebrities and press as it did to consumers.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"900\"]}},\"932\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"902\",\"901\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"933\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Merchandise\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Bespoke 747 branding was created for all merch from welcome packs to hoodies and celebrity specials. Customisation stations created with our modular branding allowed attendees to create their own through touch screen monitors, creating personal variations for keeps.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"924\"]}},\"964\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"948\",\"950\",\"943\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"935\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Fresh Produce\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Custom print shoes, each cut out of larger graphics and built by robots on the spot, delivered \\u2018fresh\\u2019 produce straight to consumers in an innovative first from the brand.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"951\"]}},\"965\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"952\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"966\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"945\",\"953\",\"944\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"936\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Basketball\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Branding played an integral role to the main spectacle of the whole weekend. The Hip-Hop&nbsp;East vs West Basketball game.&nbsp;Played on a bespoke court and terraces, with each team of stars sporting their own custom kits.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"946\"]}},\"967\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"954\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"968\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"956\",\"957\",\"955\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}}},\"37\":[\"885\"],\"51\":\"top\",\"36\":\"full\",\"35\":\"2018\"}}', '2018-03-07 09:22:51', '2018-03-07 09:22:51', '5fc11938-2299-4b26-9d65-c53514470f3b'),
 ('622', '830', '2', '1', 'en_us', '11', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Burberry\",\"slug\":\"burberry\",\"postDate\":1520414598,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"34\":\"Burberry\",\"4\":{\"831\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"822\",\"845\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"849\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"brief\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Ideation and creative direction for an online experience with standout visual imagery to elevate the new Burberry Rainbow Capsule Collection. Conveying the product in a brave, bold and futuristic way that speaks out to a younger audience.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"827\"]}},\"850\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Reponse\",\"textContent\":\"<p>With noise surrounding the drop of every Burberry collection, Superimpose decided to take the creative in a new direction most luxury brands shy away from. We created visual content to live in a virtual time capsule - a space to revisit, experience the clothing, memories and energy that came with it.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Producing a shoot packed with personality, energy and youthfulness, we then ripped up the rule book of how to showcase premium product by collaging the visuals&nbsp;together in various patterns and textures to create looks that stand out from the crowd.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"824\"]}},\"851\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"811\",\"813\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"852\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"829\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"position\":\"right\"}},\"971\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Going a step further, we developed a bank of 3D assets that showcased the Burberry patterns in a distinct way using rotating fruits and impactful slogans. Another layer was added by creating eye-catching GIFS that combined brand patterns, model movements and 3D assets.<br><br>These visuals then layered together into a unique 3D interactive experience that mimicked the the experience of a time capsule in the future - launching a showpiece for Burberry that injected the brand into new audiences through a refreshing new route.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"828\"]}},\"853\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"820\",\"812\",\"817\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"883\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"882\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"876\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"875\",\"874\",\"872\"],\"size\":\"6\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"854\":{\"type\":\"twoImagesOneImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"largeImage\":[\"838\"],\"smallImages\":[\"846\",\"848\"],\"position\":\"largeImageLeft\"}},\"855\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"826\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"856\":{\"type\":\"twoImagesOneImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"largeImage\":[\"819\"],\"smallImages\":[\"847\",\"837\"],\"position\":\"largeImageRight\"}},\"972\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"823\",\"836\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}}},\"37\":[\"811\"],\"51\":\"top\",\"36\":\"half\",\"35\":\"2018\"}}', '2018-03-07 09:23:19', '2018-03-07 09:23:19', 'f9bc32ef-2f5e-4f66-86e8-254db3e033b5'),
