 stand alone as well as integrate with each other. Treating graphics and iconography as \\u2018collectables\\u2019, attendees could create their own versions of 747 merchandise and apparel.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"896\"]}},\"928\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"895\",\"886\",\"894\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"929\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Results\",\"textContent\":\"<p>#747WarehouseSt was mentioned 6x more than Nike\\u2019s #makersofthegame during All-Star weekend, with over 20k attendees to the event. It led above all brands with 42% share of voice over the 30 day span around NBA All-Star, achieving a monumental outcome for adidas\\u2019 ASW history.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"986\"]}},\"930\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":\"\",\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"931\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Stage\",\"textContent\":\"<p>The yearly NBA All-Star Weekend is one of the noisiest moments in the global sport and cultural calendar. The objective was to launch 747 Warehouse in Los Angeles into the forefront of everyone\\u2019s minds through a bold, unapologetic and customisable brand identity and incredible creative activations that appeal as much to the celebrities and press as it did to consumers.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"900\"]}},\"932\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"902\",\"901\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"933\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Merchandise\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Bespoke 747 branding was created for all merch from welcome packs to hoodies and celebrity specials. Customisation stations created with our modular branding allowed attendees to create their own through touch screen monitors, creating personal variations for keeps.<\\/p>\",\"position\"