y specials. Customisation stations created with our modular branding allowed attendees to create their own through touch screen monitors, creating personal variations for keeps.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"924\"]}},\"964\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"992\",\"950\",\"995\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"935\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Fresh Produce\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Custom print shoes, each cut out of larger graphics and built by robots on the spot, delivered \\u2018fresh\\u2019 produce straight to consumers in an innovative first from the brand.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"951\"]}},\"965\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"952\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"966\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"945\",\"953\",\"944\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"936\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Basketball\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Branding played an integral role to the main spectacle of the whole weekend. The Hip-Hop&nbsp;East vs West Basketball game.&nbsp;Played on a bespoke court and terraces, with each team of stars sporting their own custom kits.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"946\"]}},\"967\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"954\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"968\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"955\",\"957\",\"987\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}}},\"37\":[\"885\"],\"51\":\"top\",\"36\":\"full\",\"35\":\"2018\"}}', '2018-03-07 10:23:39', '2018-03-07 10:23:39', '12e857bc-e04b-41f2-b87c-df93ccb3c815'),
