ide as they come to terms with the notion of being reactive, existing in a climate of \'opt in\\u2019 or \\u2018opt out\'. Nobody is falling in line and simply doing as told. Where once a systemic framework drove the formation, cohesion and continued existence of an ecosystem, that same framework is now being broken, and new bridges being built, in a way that will radically alter the way our consumptive society functions, if not transforming it altogether. Indeed, many old institutions have already been caught out and forced to change the foundations of their ideas and communications. Others, too slow to react and too complacent in the status quo, have collapsed entirely.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br>Major changes are happening inside the old hierarchies that once arranged and organised our society. The \\u201cascending authority\\u201d \\u2013 younger generations leading trends and movements from the bottom up \\u2013 are now becoming astute listeners, confident decision makers and pragmatic movers. From magazine publications and fashion houses to tech circles and even political parties, the old guard is waking up to an uncomfortable proposition; prepare for replacement, by choice or by force. The new wave has opened the door and is in the boardroom, and they\\u2019re not there to gain a better view. They\\u2019re there to hold their own conversation, and to keep the door open for the next group.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"981\":{\"type\":\"pullQuoteImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"The new wave has opened the door and is in the boardroom, and they\\u2019re not there to gain a better view.\",\"file\":[\"939\"],\"size\":\"medium\"}},\"982\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>In 2018, we may have reached the year that marks the beginning of the next phase; the \\u2018post-ascending authority\\u2019. Young people and marginalised groups\\u2019 cultural takeover is no longer the next phase; it is the norm. This year began with unease and turbulence, but it is within this instability that we acclimatise and evolve. <\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>So, the big question is this: Now that the youth have found themselves finally in a position to shape the future, what does that future look like?<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"984\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Stay tuned for a series of responses to come from industry thought leaders.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"983\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h2>DOING THINGS DIFFERENTLY&nbsp;<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Services Unknown is an open-ended Superimpose Studio project that facilitates new ideas, discussion, events and product.<\\/em><\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\"}}},\"52\":\"Dominance hierarchy is a phenomenon in which a clear hierarchy is established within a social group, often through aggression or force. Once a dominance hierarchy is established, the dominant group will often create a social ranking system to designate how, where and when members of different social groups may interact. These ranking systems apportion different levels of value to people in different groups, who will then have to compete for access to resources, services and opportunities. \\r\\n\",\"37\":[\"941\"]}}', '2018-03-07 11:50:28', '2018-03-07 11:50:28', '71c85eb3-ee36-4f13-9090-ce23aa5dd27b'),
 ('647', '833', '2', '1', 'en_us', '23', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"#747warehousest\",\"slug\":\"747warehousest\",\"postDate\":1520414700,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"34\":\"adidas\",\"4\":{\"925\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"885\",\"888\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"862\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"BRIEF\",\"textContent\":\"<p>The yearly NBA All-Star Weekend is one of the noisiest moments in the global sport and cultural calendar. The objective was to launch&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/maps.google.com\\/?q=747+Warehouse&entry=gmail&source=g\\\">747 Warehouse<\\/a>&nbsp;in Los Angeles into the forefront of everyone\\u2019s minds through a bold, unapologetic and customisable brand identity and incredible activations that appeal as much to the celebrities and press as it did to consumers.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"958\"]}},\"927\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Response\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Superimpose Studio led the creative concept and art direction of a \\u2018\\u2019No Rules\\u2019 approach that drove the brand language and visual identity across this competitive period - setting it apart from the usual NBA&nbsp;All-Star Weekend&nbsp;offerings and cementing the legacy of adidas as a creator\\u2019s brand.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br>The anti-corporate aesthetic carried throughout the entire space: immersive installations for product collaborations, machines building individualised footwear&nbsp;on the spot, test centres to show off your skills, the Sound Lab, the Stage and Creator Pop-up customisation stations as well as building walls, and floor takedowns.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br>Mimicking a sticker pack of assets, the experience was created purposefully to allow visual elements to stand alone as well as integrate with each other. Treating graphics and iconography as \\u2018collectables\\u2019, attendees could create their own versions of 747 merchandise and apparel.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"896\"]}},\"991\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/258818655\",\"thumbnail\":\"\"}},\"928\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"895\",\"994\",\"894\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"929\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Results\",\"textContent\":\"<p>#747WarehouseSt was mentioned 6x more than Nike\\u2019s #makersofthegame during All-Star weekend, with over 20k attendees to the event. It led above all brands with 42% share of voice over the 30 day span around NBA All-Star, achieving a monumental outcome for adidas\\u2019 ASW history.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"986\"]}},\"930\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":\"\",\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"931\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Stage\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Impactful digital projections and visual content appeared on the main stages hosting global artists such as Kanye West, Kid Cudi, Pusha-T and Childish Gambino.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"900\"]}},\"932\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"902\",\"901\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"933\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Merchandise\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Bespoke 747 branding was created for all merch from welcome packs to hoodies and celebrity specials. Customisation stations created with our modular branding allowed attendees to create their own through touch screen monitors, creating personal variations for keeps.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"924\"]}},\"964\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"992\",\"950\",\"995\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"935\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Fresh Produce\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Custom print shoes, each cut out of larger graphics and built by robots on the spot, delivered \\u2018fresh\\u2019 produce straight to consumers in an innovative first from the brand.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\",\"image\":[\"951\"]}},\"965\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"952\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"966\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"996\",\"953\",\"944\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"936\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Basketball\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Branding played an integral role to the main spectacle of the whole weekend. The Hip-Hop&nbsp;East vs West Basketball game.&nbsp;Played on a bespoke court and terraces, with each team of stars sporting their own custom kits.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"946\"]}},\"967\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"954\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"968\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"955\",\"957\",\"987\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}}},\"37\":[\"885\"],\"51\":\"top\",\"36\":\"full\",\"35\":\"2018\"}}', '2018-03-07 12:21:48', '2018-03-07 12:21:48', '35b1955d-0bae-460a-bee2-90f0a0d3e543'),
 ('648', '798', '2', '1', 'en_us', '21', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"adidas Originals by Neighborhood\",\"slug\":\"neighborhood\",\"postDate\":1520414580,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"34\":\"adidas Originals\",\"4\":{\"801\":{\"type\":\"video\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"videoUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/youtu.be\\/8h9iMMv0ETs\",\"thumbnail\":[\"785\"]}},\"799\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"783\",\"769\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"800\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"BRIEF\",\"textContent\":\"<p>adidas Originals by Neighborhood is one of the most revered collaborations on the planet. Superimpose were briefed with&nbsp;creating&nbsp;an eclectic campaign that celebrates the collaboration\\u2019s core inspiration of the traditional Japanese Shinsengumi, whilst making it relevant for today\'s audience.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"782\"]}},\"802\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Response\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Rejecting the expected approach of shooting the collection\\u2019s inspirations with a nostalgic lens, Superimpose focused on key traits from the Shinsengumi such as the \\u2018ride or die\\u2019 collective attitude they had for each other and their unique way of fusing eastern and western&nbsp;styles.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"778\"]}},\"803\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"765\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"804\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"784\",\"779\",\"776\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"805\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"773\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"806\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"textContent\":\"<p>Bringing these values into the present and pushing into the future, we showcased what the contemporary Shinsengumi looks like by integrating the diverse mix of styles and race that encapsulate the new generation.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Delivered in a visually striking film that heightens the senses and puts the squad mentality at the forefront of the story, we created an accompanying lookbook that elevated the product from a global perspective<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"881\"]}},\"878\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"793\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"808\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"792\",\"787\",\"790\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"865\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"OUTCOME\",\"textContent\":\"<p>The film and photography premiered at a series of launch parties from LA to Tokyo, whilst pop-up stores delivered the product to the consumer ending with the entire collection achieving global sell-out.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"left\",\"image\":[\"767\"]}},\"809\":{\"type\":\"imageSet\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"860\",\"858\"],\"size\":\"12\",\"alignment\":\"\"}},\"810\":{\"type\":\"singleImage\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"766\"],\"size\":\"autoHeight\",\"position\":\"center\"}}},\"37\":[\"765\"],\"51\":\"top\",\"36\":\"full\",\"35\":\"2018\"}}', '2018-03-07 12:22:15', '2018-03-07 12:22:15', '39981801-245c-4272-85b5-06c742864c6c'),
