 ('661', '1022', '4', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"EMOTICASH: FINANCE WITH FEELING\",\"slug\":\"emoticash-finance-with-feeling\",\"postDate\":null,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"53\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Using the latest Emotional Detection and Recognition (EDR) technology, we provide brands and media companies with your reactions to their products, all through the camera in your phone. In exchange, your responses equate to Emoticash, which you can spend on self-care activities and products such as Gong Baths, Yoga and meditation sessions. Paid to smile. Paid to frown. Paid to be you.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1021\"],\"size\":\"large\"}}},\"52\":\"Welcome to Emoticash, where we bring your feelings into the equation. We believe that consumers should be rewarded for sharing their emotional data, ___________. It takes 26 muscles to smile, or 62 to frown. We accept either as payment.\",\"37\":[\"1020\"]}}', '2018-03-22 23:19:48', '2018-03-22 23:19:48', '8de63043-7336-4749-821f-2075673dcd4c'),
