zzwords and adspend and data and digital strategies, as much as established authorities and systems will always inevitably co-opt, appropriate and monetize their trends and tastes. They move fast. It\\u2019s an endless cycle but the more interesting, ascending, challenging cultural spaces and stories are swallowed up by the existing structure, the more there will always have to be something even newer, younger, fresher, stranger, more stimulating, more marginal to keep moving onto.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1142\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1141\"],\"size\":\"medium\"}},\"1140\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>As much as we hype it, there is no big new structural revolution that\\u2019s suddenly happening to culture because of millennials, smartphones and the internet. But cool weird creative kids never needed one, they were the revolution. They still are. Variables may change, but the struggle stays infinite.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1143\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<h2>DOING THINGS DIFFERENTLY&nbsp;<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Services Unknown is an open-ended Superimpose Studio project that facilitates new ideas, discussion, events and product.<br><br><\\/em><\\/p><p>Read Post-Ascending Authority&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/superimpose.studio\\/post\\/post-asscending-authority\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">here<\\/a>.\\r\\n<br>Read response #1 from Harry Benson <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/superimpose.studio\\/post\\/paa-response1\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">here.<\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Submission of new ideas and responses can be received at&nbsp;<a href=\\\"mailto:hello@superimpose.studio\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">hello@superimpose.studio<\\/a><\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}}},\"52\":\"The first response to our \'Post-Ascending Authority\' statement from Services Unknown comes from Silk Agency founder and freelance Writer Lillian He.\",\"37\":[\"1128\"]}}', '2018-04-30 09:01:06', '2018-04-30 09:01:06', '0ed6cd9e-8af3-442f-8f7b-abe53725837f'),
