\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1205\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1211\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1179\"],\"size\":\"small\"}}},\"52\":\"\",\"37\":[\"1212\"]}}', '2018-06-19 10:36:33', '2018-06-19 10:36:33', 'd755605b-8522-498d-b6a6-cfe359a62886'),
 ('815', '1176', '4', '1', 'en_us', '13', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"NO MORE GODS.\",\"slug\":\"no-more-gods-icee-festival-2018\",\"postDate\":1529336280,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"53\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1177\"],\"size\":\"medium\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>No More Gods. The state of flux the consumer landscape has been in has now gone into overdrive. Driven by the new consumer, this is the most exciting time in our industry. The rulebooks are being ripped up, barriers torn down and traditional power is being displaced.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1189\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1175\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"new3\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Post-Ascending Authority is a term Superimpose coined back in 2016, when we identified a shift of power in traditional hierarchies and new attitudes being born, all being driven by a new generation of creators.<br><br>This new generation is&nbsp;predomitly&nbsp;made up of 16-24 years, although age doesn\'t define them. In fact they defy any traditional definition from borders to sex to language.<\\/p><p>In previous generations - power, trends and decision making was all communicated and driven from the top (us) down to the consumer&nbsp;(them). This is no longer the case. The new consumer have all the tools to do it from themselves, the flow of power has flipped. The&nbsp;first generation to truly capitalise on this, they&nbsp;listen to their friends over brands, their&nbsp;trust in traditional institutions&nbsp;has fallen away and they are the creating the future without any dictation.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1190\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1187\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"new4\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Why does all of this truly matter?&nbsp;Well to put it in simple terms, they will become the most influential demographic in the world in every aspect, if they are not already.<\\/p><p>Population, access to technology, spending power - they hold the key to everything and are using it in ways never seen before.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1207\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1206\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1191\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1186\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1192\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1185\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1193\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1184\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1194\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1183\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1195\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1167\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1196\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1182\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1197\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1168\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1198\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1169\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1199\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1181\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1200\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1170\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1201\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1171\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1202\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1172\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1208\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1203\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1209\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1204\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1210\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1205\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1211\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1179\"],\"size\":\"small\"}}},\"52\":\"Live at ICEE Festival 2018.\\r\\n\\r\\n\'No More Gods: Dispelling industry myths and doing it differently\'\\r\\n\\r\\nRejecting the traditional industry set up, Superimpose gives insight on how they became a global game changer ripping up the rule book and ignoring the \\u2018how to\\u2019s\\u2019 to do it right in advertising. A foray into the new world order; subverting hierarchies and embracing collaboration and community, they will also profile the most exciting case studies with a unique glimpse into their creative thinking process making waves cross industry, starting movements across country and garnering cult agency status.\",\"37\":[\"1212\"]}}', '2018-06-19 12:40:24', '2018-06-19 12:40:24', '57e58c0a-c1f0-4db1-aa18-d7daafd44fd1'),
 ('816', '1176', '4', '1', 'en_us', '14', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"NO MORE GODS.\",\"slug\":\"no-more-gods-icee-festival-2018\",\"postDate\":1529336280,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"53\":{\"1213\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1177\"],\"size\":\"medium\"}},\"1214\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>No More Gods. This constant&nbsp;state of flux the consumer landscape has been in for the past 5-10 years&nbsp;has now gone into overdrive. Driven by the new consumer, this is the most exciting time in our industry. The rulebooks are being ripped up, barriers torn down and traditional power is being displaced.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1189\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1175\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1215\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Post-Ascending Authority is a term Superimpose coined back in 2016, when we identified a shift of power in traditional hierarchies and new attitudes being born, all being driven by a new generation of creators.<br><br>This new generation is&nbsp;predomitly&nbsp;made up of 16-24 years, although age doesn\'t define them. In fact they defy any traditional definition from borders to sex to language.<br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>In previous generations - power, trends and decision making was all communicated and driven from the top (us) down to the consumer&nbsp;(them). This is no longer the case. The new consumer have all the tools to do it from themselves, the flow of power has flipped. The&nbsp;first generation to truly capitalise on this, they&nbsp;listen to their friends over brands, their&nbsp;trust in traditional institutions&nbsp;has fallen away and they are the creating the future without any dictation.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1190\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1187\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1216\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Why does all of this truly matter?&nbsp;Well to put it in simple terms, they will become the most influential demographic in the world in every aspect, if they are not already.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Population, access to technology, spending power - they hold the key to everything and are using it in ways never seen before.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1207\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1206\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Nobody should underestimate this huge consumer shift in thinking and attitude. IT will change not only advertising as we know it, but also society as a whole from fashion to music and the arts to politics.&nbsp;<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>No corner is safe from this disruption, there is nowhere for the Gods to hide. It\'s time to open up or face being booted out and rolled over.<br><br><br>Disruptive has been the buzzword of the last few years, but are we as an industry truly ready for what that means in our day to day business. It may sound frightening at face value, yet&nbsp;it is truly the most exciting time to be a part of this industry.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1191\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1186\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>All of this change, the subverting of power and&nbsp;ignoring traditional hierarchies all stems from the new attitude that defines this generation. They have a new way of seeing&nbsp;the world and themselves, a go getter ambition and drive that is unstoppable.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>No matter what they put their minds too, they will always find a way and not a way found in traditional textbooks. Their confidence drives their collaboration cross borders, with their online peers as they create brands, start publications and&nbsp;kick start social&nbsp;movements.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>They have a confidence never seen in previous generations and are utilising this to wield power and success in everything they do.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1192\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1185\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"new3\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>No longer are they looking for validation, no longer do they want to work for the best agency or to work in-house at the likes of adidas or Nike.<\\/p><p>They want adidas to work for them, to create their own brand, their own agency and have the powers of old collaborating on their terms. There\'s no more gods, it\'s a new set of rules.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1193\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1184\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"new4\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>It\'s exciting, the biggest shake up to date. Fuelled not by one factory but by confidence, technological access, curiosity, information and a deep lying strive for entrepreneurship.<br><br>It is really a renaissance.<br><br>With every renaissance a new way of living and working is born. The traditional \'how to\'s\' no longer exist.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1194\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1183\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1195\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1167\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1196\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1182\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1197\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1168\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1198\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1169\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1199\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1181\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1200\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1170\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1201\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1171\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1202\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1172\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1208\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1203\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1209\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1204\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1210\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1205\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1211\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1179\"],\"size\":\"small\"}}},\"52\":\"Rejecting the traditional industry set up, Superimpose gives insight on how they became a global game changer ripping up the rule book and ignoring the \\u2018how to\\u2019s\\u2019 to do it right in advertising. A foray into the new world order; subverting hierarchies and embracing collaboration and community, they will also profile the most exciting case studies with a unique glimpse into their creative thinking process making waves cross industry, starting movements across country and garnering cult agency status.\",\"37\":[\"1212\"]}}', '2018-06-19 13:28:06', '2018-06-19 13:28:06', 'e64540ee-e0dd-494d-8e2d-c7def6949a9a'),
 ('817', '1176', '4', '1', 'en_us', '15', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"NO MORE GODS.\",\"slug\":\"no-more-gods-icee-festival-2018\",\"postDate\":1529336280,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":0,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"53\":{\"1213\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1177\"],\"size\":\"medium\"}},\"1214\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>No More Gods. This constant&nbsp;state of flux the consumer landscape has been in for the past 5-10 years&nbsp;has now gone into overdrive. Driven by the new consumer, this is the most exciting time in our industry. The rulebooks are being ripped up, barriers torn down and traditional power is being displaced.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1189\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1175\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1215\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Post-Ascending Authority is a term Superimpose coined back in 2016, when we identified a shift of power in traditional hierarchies and new attitudes being born, all being driven by a new generation of creators.<br><br>This new generation is&nbsp;predomitly&nbsp;made up of 16-24 years, although age doesn\'t define them. In fact they defy any traditional definition from borders to sex to language.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>In previous generations - power, trends and decision making was all communicated and driven from the top (us) down to the consumer&nbsp;(them). This is no longer the case. The new consumer have all the tools to do it from themselves, the flow of power has flipped. The&nbsp;first generation to truly capitalise on this, they&nbsp;listen to their friends over brands, their&nbsp;trust in traditional institutions&nbsp;has fallen away and they are the creating the future without any dictation.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1190\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1187\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1216\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Why does all of this truly matter?&nbsp;Well to put it in simple terms, they will become the most influential demographic in the world in every aspect, if they are not already.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Population, access to technology, spending power - they hold the key to everything and are using it in ways never seen before.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1207\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1206\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1217\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Nobody should underestimate this huge consumer shift in thinking and attitude. IT will change not only advertising as we know it, but also society as a whole from fashion to music and the arts to politics.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>No corner is safe from this disruption, there is nowhere for the Gods to hide. It\'s time to open up or face being booted out and rolled over.<br><br><br>Disruptive has been the buzzword of the last few years, but are we as an industry truly ready for what that means in our day to day business. It may sound frightening at face value, yet&nbsp;it is truly the most exciting time to be a part of this industry.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1191\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1186\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1218\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>All of this change, the subverting of power and&nbsp;ignoring traditional hierarchies all stems from the new attitude that defines this generation. They have a new way of seeing&nbsp;the world and themselves, a go getter ambition and drive that is unstoppable.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>No matter what they put their minds too, they will always find a way and not a way found in traditional textbooks. Their confidence drives their collaboration cross borders, with their online peers as they create brands, start publications and&nbsp;kick start social&nbsp;movements.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>They have a confidence never seen in previous generations and are utilising this to wield power and success in everything they do.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1192\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1185\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1219\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>No longer are they looking for validation, no longer do they want to work for the best agency or to work in-house at the likes of adidas or Nike.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>They want adidas to work for them, to create their own brand, their own agency and have the powers of old collaborating on their terms. There\'s no more gods, it\'s a new set of rules.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1193\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1184\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1220\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>It\'s exciting, the biggest shake up to date. Fuelled not by one factory but by confidence, technological access, curiosity, information and a deep lying strive for entrepreneurship.<br><br>It is really a renaissance.<br><br>With every renaissance a new way of living and working is born. The traditional \'how to\'s\' no longer exist.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1194\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1183\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"new6\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>What does this all mean&nbsp;for the traditional career path, the trajectory to success? Everything as it is a concept no longer relevant to this generation.<br><\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1195\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1167\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"new5\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>one mentor to guide you is no longer relevant. you need multiple mentors, of all ages, cross industry, different interests.&nbsp;<\\/p><ul><li>We\\u2019re starting to see more projects & businesses that hit the intersection of football and design, art and sustainability, technology and art.&nbsp;<\\/li><li>True to no more gods, \\u2018specialisms\\u2019 aren\\u2019t about being good at one thing really well, especially when sectors are colliding and the \\u2018gods\\u2019 are out of touch<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>No linear paths<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Industries are criss crossing<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Innovation is found within experimentation<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>It\\u2019s up to us to facilitate this and remove the leash<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1196\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1182\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"new3\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>The Holy Trinity of power sitting between brand, agency and publisher is no<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1197\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1168\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"new4\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Traditional model is collapsing&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Authority, budget and power doesn\\u2019t just sit in these house now<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>And how they operate isn\\u2019t set in stone<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Now you see agencies existing in-house within brands, you see brands sponsoring suppliers, you see agencies becoming powerhouse brands themselves.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The rise of the influencer that transcends across these is a marker of the new world power play.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1198\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1169\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Milk started as a studio and now has a leading product on the market<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Basement was a Facebook group and now an agency with a hugeyouth community as part of their offering.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Kanye wants to do everything - sneakers, high fashion and most recently architecture&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Gurls Talks - influencer turned publisher<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Vice ahead of the curve and the biggest example moving from a print publication to a full scale global beeeeeast<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1199\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1181\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"new8\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>The idea that you can buy success, that money is the answer for everything is no more.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1200\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1170\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<ul>\\r\\n<li>viewers can see through paid advertising and sponsorships so clearly now<\\/li>\\r\\n<li><\\/li>\\r\\n<li>The challenge is authenticity and real meaning as competition rises, more platforms rise, and cut through is harder than ever before.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>- adidas \\/ Nike - creativity is king<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1201\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1171\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1202\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1172\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1208\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1203\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1209\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1204\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1210\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1205\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1211\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1179\"],\"size\":\"small\"}}},\"52\":\"Rejecting the traditional industry set up, Superimpose gives insight on how they became a global game changer ripping up th