ition\":\"full\"}},\"1190\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1187\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1216\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Why does all of this truly matter?&nbsp;Well to put it in simple terms, they will become the most influential demographic in the world in every aspect, if they are not already.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Population, access to technology, spending power - they hold the key to everything and are using it in ways never seen before.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1207\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1206\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1217\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Nobody should underestimate this huge consumer shift in thinking and attitude. IT will change not only advertising as we know it, but also society as a whole from fashion to music and the arts to politics.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>No corner is safe from this disruption, there is nowhere for the Gods to hide. It\'s time to open up or face being booted out and rolled over.<br><br><br>Disruptive has been the buzzword of the last few years, but are we as an industry truly ready for what that means in our day to day business. It may sound frightening at face value, yet&nbsp;it is truly the most exciting time to be a part of this industry.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1191\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1186\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1218\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>All of this change, the subverting of power and&nbsp;ignoring traditional hierarchies all stems from the new attitude that defines this generation. They have a new way of seeing&nbsp;the world and themselves, a go getter ambition and drive that is unstoppable.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>No matter what they put their minds too, they will always find a way and not a way found in traditional textbooks. Their confidence drives their collaboration cross borders, with their online peers as they create brands, start publications and&nbsp;kick start social&nbsp;movements.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>They have a confidence never seen in previous generations and are utilising this to wield power and success in everything they do.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1192\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1185\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1219\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>No longer are they looking for validation, no longer do they want to work for the best agency or to work in-house at the likes of adidas or Nike.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>They want adidas to work for them, to create their own brand, their own agency and have the powers of old collaborating on their terms. There\'s no more gods, it\'s a new set of rules.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1193\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1184\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1220\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>It\'s exciting, the biggest shake up to date. Fuelled not by one factory but by confidence, technological access, curiosity, information and a deep lying strive for entrepreneurship.<br><br>It is really a renaissance.<br><br>With every renaissance a new way of living and working is born. The traditional \'how to\'s\' no longer exist.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1194\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1183\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1221\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>What does this all mean&nbsp;for the traditional career path, the trajectory to success? Everything as it is a concept no longer relevant to this generation.<br><\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1195\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1167\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1222\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Insert Text<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1196\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1182\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1223\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>The Holy Trinity of power sitting between brand, agency and publisher is no<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1197\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1168\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1224\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Insert Text<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1198\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1169\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1225\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1199\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1181\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1226\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>The idea that you can buy success, that money is the answer for everything is no more.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1200\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1170\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1227\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<ul><li>Insert Text<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1201\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1171\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1228\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Insert Text<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1202\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1172\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1229\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Insert Text about this is how we act.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1208\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1203\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1230\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Insert small text<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1209\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1204\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1231\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Insert small text.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1210\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1205\"],\"size\":\"small\"}},\"1232\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Insert small text<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1211\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1179\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"1233\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>So how do we move forward and work within this industry changing shift?<br><br>For us we believe it is simply to never become complacent, never act like a God. We need to be open to change and willing to be challenged. With the pace of change that is happening across consumers, cultures and attitudes, it is important to collaborate and be open to new ideas from any angle.<br><br>Only through ability to become adaptable and open can we truly make creative work that is exciting, relevant and&nbsp;authentic.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>It\'s truly the most exciting time to be in the industry, it\'s time to open up the doors or face being left behind.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}}},\"52\":\"Rejecting the traditional industry set up, Superimpose gives insight on how they became a global game changer ripping up the rule book and ignoring the \\u2018how to\\u2019s\\u2019 to do it right in advertising. A foray into the new world order; subverting hierarchies and embracing collaboration and community, they will also profile the most exciting case studies with a unique glimpse into their creative thinking process making waves cross industry, starting movements across country and garnering cult agency