ration and twist it for themselves with no collaboration or consultation.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br>As we\'ve seen with the likes of @diet_prada and the backlash those campaigns all faced, this is the call-out generation. No matter how much money you have or how big your brand is, success is not a given. No longer will the consumer follow blindly what a brand tells them.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\"}},\"1211\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1179\"],\"size\":\"large\"}},\"1233\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>So how do we move forward and work within this industry changing shift?<br><br>For us we believe it is simply to never become complacent, never act like a God. We need to be open to change and willing to be challenged. With the pace of change that is happening across consumers, cultures and attitudes, it is important to collaborate and be open to new ideas from any angle.<br><br>Only through ability to become adaptable and open can we truly make creative work that is exciting, relevant and&nbsp;authentic.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>It\'s truly the most exciting time to be in the industry, it\'s time to open up the doors or face being left behind.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"right\"}}},\"52\":\"\\\"No more Gods: Dispelling industry myths and doing things differently\\\" as presented at ICEE Festival 2018.\",\"37\":[\"1212\"]}}', '2018-06-19 16:57:19', '2018-06-19 16:57:19', '60db2e02-4bc2-4bc4-ad22-4ad586090c9a'),
