when brands try to act like the Gods. Aiming to take a narrative true to this generation and twist it for themselves with no collaboration or consultation.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br>As we\'ve seen with the likes of @diet_prada and the backlash those campaigns all faced, this is the call-out generation. No matter how much money you have or how big your brand is, success is not a given. No longer will the consumer follow blindly what a brand tells them.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1211\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1179\"],\"size\":\"medium\"}},\"1233\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>So how do we move forward and work within this industry changing shift?<br><br>For us we believe it is simply to never become complacent, never act like a God. We need to be open to change and willing to be challenged. With the pace of change that is happening across consumers, cultures and attitudes, it is important to collaborate and be open to new ideas from any angle.<br><br>Only through ability to become adaptable and open can we truly make creative work that is exciting, relevant and&nbsp;authentic.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>It\'s truly the most exciting time to be in the industry, it\'s time to open up the doors or face being left behind.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}}},\"52\":\"\\\"No more Gods: Dispelling industry myths and doing things differently\\\" as presented at ICEE Festival 2018.\",\"37\":[\"1212\"]}}', '2018-06-19 16:58:10', '2018-06-19 16:58:10', '579f05a5-cf6e-422c-8acc-eeb878114dc4'),
 ('831', '1176', '4', '1', 'en_us', '29', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"NO MORE GODS.\",\"slug\":\"no-more-gods-icee-festival-2018\",\"postDate\":1529336280,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"53\":{\"1213\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":\"\",\"size\":\"medium\"}},\"1214\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>No More Gods. &nbsp;The consumer landscape has been in a&nbsp;constant state of flux&nbsp;for the past 5-10 years, yet now it has&nbsp;gone into overdrive and change is here. <br><br><br>Driven by the new consumer, this is the most exciting time in our industry. The rulebooks are being ripped up, barriers torn down and traditional power is being displaced.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1189\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1175\"],\"size\":\"medium\"}},\"1215\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Post-Ascending Authority is a term Superimpose coined back in 2016, when we identified a shift of power in traditional hierarchies and new attitudes being born, all being driven by a new generation of creators.<br><br><br>This new generation is&nbsp;predominantly&nbsp;made up of those aged&nbsp;16-24, although age doesn\'t define them. In fact they defy any traditional definition from borders to sex to language.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>In previous generations - power, trends and decision making was all communicated and driven from the top (us) down to the consumer&nbsp;(them). This is no longer the case. The new consumer have all the tools to do it from themselves, the flow of power has flipped. The&nbsp;first generation to truly capitalise on this, they&nbsp;listen to their friends over brands, their&nbsp;trust in traditional institutions&nbsp;has fallen away and they are the creating the future without any dictation.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1190\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1187\"],\"size\":\"medium\"}},\"1216\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Why does all of this truly matter?&nbsp;Well to put it in simple terms, they will become the most influential demographic in the world in every aspect, if they are not already.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Population, access to technology, spending power - they hold the key to everything and are using it in ways never seen before.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1207\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1206\"],\"size\":\"medium\"}},\"1217\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Nobody should underestimate this huge consumer shift in thinking and attitude. IT will change not only advertising as we know it, but also society as a whole from fashion to music and the arts to politics.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>No corner is safe from this disruption, there is nowhere for the Gods to hide. It\'s time to open up or face being booted out and rolled over.<br><br><br>Disruptive has been the buzzword of the last few years, but are we as an industry truly ready for what that means in our day to day business. It may sound frightening at face value, yet&nbsp;it is truly the most exciting time to be a part of this industry.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1191\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1186\"],\"size\":\"medium\"}},\"1218\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>All of this change, the subverting of power and&nbsp;ignoring 