py\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>The Holy Trinity of power sitting between brand, agency and publisher is no longer.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1197\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1168\"],\"size\":\"medium\"}},\"1225\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>Where once brands, agencies and publishers held all the power and had an impermeable model that seemed to withstand new entrants and pulls on their dynamic, these houses can no longer stand the tectonic shift that gives way to the influencer. The phenomenon which allows every individual, brand or business to create desire moves simultaneously in line with cross collaboration, mergers, acquisitions and sponsorships. You can be anything, as long as you don\\u2019t fake i<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1199\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1181\"],\"size\":\"medium\"}},\"1226\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>The idea that you can buy success, that money is the answer for everything no longer rings true.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"center\"}},\"1200\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1170\"],\"size\":\"medium\"}},\"1227\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>More content, more platforms and more competition. Bigger budgets doesn\\u2019t guarantee bigger reach. The rise of digital media has advanced our ability to decipher between paid promotions, \\u2019native\\u2019 advertising and authentic content.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br>The challenge is authentic storytelling and finding new ways of cutting through. How does your message stand out amongst the feed? Why does it matter to the individual?<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1201\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1171\"],\"size\":\"medium\"}},\"1228\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>However, being creative and daring requires you to be considerate and pragmatic. Pepsi, Puma &&nbsp;Dove are just a snapshot of what can go wrong when brands try to act like the Gods. Aiming to take a narrative true to this generation and twist it for themselves with no collaboration or consultation.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br>As we\'ve seen with the likes of @diet_prada and the backlash those campaigns all faced, this is the call-out generation. No matter how much money you have or how big your brand is, success is not a given. No longer will the consumer follow blindly what a brand tells them.<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}},\"1211\":{\"type\":\"image\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"file\":[\"1179\"],\"size\":\"medium\"}},\"1233\":{\"type\":\"copy\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"copy\":\"<p>So how do we move forward and work within this industry changing shift?<br><br>For us we believe it is simply to never become complacent, never act like a God. We need to be open to change and willing to be challenged. With the pace of change that is happening across consumers, cultures and attitudes, it is important to collaborate and be open to new ideas from any angle.<br><br>Only through ability to become adaptable and open can we truly make creative work that is exciting, relevant and&nbsp;authentic.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>It\'s truly the most exciting time to be in the industry, it\'s time to open up the doors or face being left behind.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"position\":\"full\"}}},\"52\":\"\\\"No more Gods: Dispelling industry myths and doing things differently\\\" as presented at ICEE Festival 2018.\",\"37\":[\"1212\"]}}', '2018-06-19 17:00:38', '2018-06-19 17:00:38', 'baf61039-ef52-48b8-a166-98185105582e'),
