 ('15', '56', 'en_us', '<p>Create a lookbook to launch the premium Primeknit Tubular X, as a development for adidas Originals Tubular range.</p>', 'center', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'BRIEF', NULL, NULL, '2016-07-12 11:21:06', '2017-04-24 11:08:41', '0a9b3935-267d-45e6-8482-3a713ff7f4c8'),
