 ('123', '291', 'en_us', '<p>Create a set shoot to elevate the product silhouettes and detail in the new White Mountaineering footwear collaboration</p>', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Brief:', NULL, NULL, '2017-01-11 16:19:25', '2017-04-25 13:21:40', 'd05ee773-c694-44ea-a05a-3f7af2716241'),
 ('128', '318', 'en_us', '<p>The shoes were shot on a sharp angular set which allowed the personality of the shoes to shine, while maintaining a premium, high-end design feel that the collaboration created.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Response', NULL, NULL, '2017-02-28 13:51:55', '2017-04-25 13:21:40', '4a38d256-7688-47b9-8902-210634d02b11'),
 ('129', '319', 'en_us', '<p>We shot the two shoe models on an abstract, dark background that evoked sheet metal. This allowed us to construct compositions that would bring to life the gritty, dark, abstract personality of Mastermind Japan while also highlighting the product detailing.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Response', NULL, NULL, '2017-02-28 14:08:39', '2017-04-24 11:08:53', '4e849839-654c-4879-8c5d-be1380a915ea'),
 ('130', '320', 'en_us', '<p>For the second drop of Pharrell’s ‘Pink Beach’ collaboration with adidas Originals, we were asked to lead creative on the kids takedown shoot.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'BRIEF', NULL, NULL, '2017-02-28 14:43:39', '2017-04-24 11:09:11', 'ec6b50c5-bcb9-40a1-9e29-4fc06620c77a'),
 ('131', '321', 'en_us', '<p>We translated the style, attitude and playfulness from the adult shoot into an aesthetic that worked for a kid’s collection.</p>', 'center', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Response', NULL, NULL, '2017-02-28 14:43:39', '2017-04-24 11:09:11', '5890cfdf-bfcd-4326-be23-371c8c44dbfe'),
 ('132', '322', 'en_us', '<p>With a strong focus on the styling, we set out to make the collection appeal to a wider audience set by juxtaposing the shoe with a series of different looks designed to appeal to multiple subcultures and tribes in the target market.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'RESPONSE', NULL, NULL, '2017-02-28 14:53:42', '2017-04-24 11:08:41', 'a797b522-30c9-4e2e-8cab-0d956566b706'),
 ('133', '323', 'en_us', '<p>With extensive knowledge of the target consumer mindset and their interests, Superimpose delivered a creative that combined this with influences from Bape’s Japanese streetwear scene roots and the iconic street style images often seen in classic, early 00s issues of The Face and i-D.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Delivering simple shots in a multitude of close up crops, we showcased product detail and were able to put across the emotion and attitude that the collaboration represents.<br></p>', 'center', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'RESPONSE', NULL, NULL, '2017-02-28 14:57:37', '2017-04-25 13:20:57', '75a4bd4a-afbe-4265-94da-895af96906f1'),
 ('134', '324', 'en_us', '<p>Build on the success of previous seasons by creating a brand personality for adidas Originals eyewear.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'BRIEF', NULL, NULL, '2017-02-28 15:03:22', '2017-04-24 11:10:46', '08d40ec8-937b-410f-bfda-4c859d542831'),
