 ('190', '622', 'en_us', '<p>In the final instalment of a collaboration series between adidas Originals and Pusha T, Superimpose Studio had to elevate the story behind the ‘Bodega Babies’ EQT ADV shoe, drawing inspiration from the product and Pusha T’s coming of age around his local place of importance to create a compelling film.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Brief', NULL, NULL, '2017-11-01 12:12:32', '2017-11-07 10:35:43', '92ca215e-f669-43dd-aca6-feda1d09f3a6'),
