 ('224', '800', 'en_us', '<p>adidas Originals by Neighborhood is one of the most revered collaborations on the planet. Superimpose were briefed with&nbsp;creating&nbsp;an eclectic campaign that celebrates the collaboration’s core inspiration of the traditional Japanese Shinsengumi, whilst making it relevant for today\'s audience.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'BRIEF', NULL, NULL, '2018-03-05 13:20:48', '2018-03-07 12:22:15', '6a9858ac-9e32-4132-a3f1-4eb581ef8027'),
 ('225', '801', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://youtu.be/8h9iMMv0ETs', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2018-03-05 13:20:48', '2018-03-07 12:22:15', 'a341fc1d-8f34-432c-9503-68b6eee33cfb'),
 ('226', '802', 'en_us', '<p>Rejecting the expected approach of shooting the collection’s inspirations with a nostalgic lens, Superimpose focused on key traits from the Shinsengumi such as the ‘ride or die’ collective attitude they had for each other and their unique way of fusing eastern and western&nbsp;styles.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Response', NULL, NULL, '2018-03-05 13:30:50', '2018-03-07 12:22:15', '11ccd94d-0082-41ba-bdee-9b60f0930fa5'),
 ('227', '803', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, '12', 'center', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2018-03-05 13:30:50', '2018-03-07 12:22:15', '65d3acf9-cbcd-40e0-8510-0e4ab596f09e'),
 ('228', '804', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '12', '', '2018-03-05 13:30:50', '2018-03-07 12:22:15', '53bf31b4-f641-40ac-8998-13bf999a8ecb'),
 ('229', '805', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, '12', 'center', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2018-03-05 13:30:50', '2018-03-07 12:22:15', '91c36ace-596b-49ce-bcc8-56b0e9459eef'),
 ('230', '806', 'en_us', '<p>Bringing these values into the present and pushing into the future, we showcased what the contemporary Shinsengumi looks like by integrating the diverse mix of styles and race that encapsulate the new generation.<br></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Delivered in a visually striking film that heightens the senses and puts the squad mentality at the forefront of the story, we created an accompanying lookbook that elevated the product from a global perspective</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '2018-03-05 13:30:50', '2018-03-07 12:22:15', '7025660e-5212-4179-8366-9e0670dea107'),
