 ('55', '520', 'en_us', '<p>The showcase spanned across various forms of art and media, from graphics, fabrics, animation to photography and sound, with attendees having the opportunity to view, interact and take a piece of the work home.  <br /><br />With hundreds of people coming together to one space from all corners of the industry and beyond, we sparked conversation, criticism, and a new discourse for the future.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'full', '2017-10-24 16:17:59', '2017-11-06 17:02:33', 'c124949b-1582-4f5e-b5d7-ff9b13ebe9d9'),
